(27, 729, 'George', 'george.olaru@pixelgrade.com', 'http://pixelgrade.com', '5.2.190.30', '2015-10-26 08:19:43', '2015-10-26 08:19:43', 'First class service and great modern Italian food. My pal and I had lunch here and despite the place buzzing on a Friday and very busy. Lovely room, modern, stylish decor, this place has just got it ''right'' and delivers a smart, professional and delicious dining experience. Recommended!', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
