(29, 864, 'Alin', 'alin.clamba@yahoo.com', '', '79.114.43.127', '2015-10-30 18:29:17', '2015-10-30 18:29:17', 'This was a really good way to see London. 21st birthday treat. Great combination of sightseeing and speed. Recommended!! Great banter from guide Rory and excellent side dips at speed from Nick. Great trip guys! Thanks!', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(30, 1013, 'Vlad Olaru', 'vlad.olaru@pixelgrade.com', '', '5.2.190.30', '2015-11-13 10:36:56', '2015-11-13 10:36:56', 'Despite having lived practically next door for the past year, i''ve only recently visited this lovely eatery. I''ve definitely been missing out. Charm, style, good food, excellent service and a real commitment in supporting various charities and the local community have made The Haberdashery my new favourite local.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(31, 118, 'Serban', 'serban.costandache@pixelgrade.com', '', '5.2.190.30', '2015-11-06 17:27:14', '2015-11-06 17:27:14', 'This is a very small intimate restaurant and the food service and ambiance are excellent.We enjoyed all the food served from quite a small open kitchen area and would certainly recommend this restaurant to anyone visiting the area.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(32, 128, 'Michael', 'michael@pixelgrade.com', '', '5.2.190.30', '2015-11-06 17:12:39', '2015-11-06 17:12:39', 'I took my girlfriend to Jago for her birthday on a colleague''s recommendation and it was a great evening. The space itself is really cool and the service was friendly and accommodating. The food was excellent and surprisingly affordable considering the location and quality of the restaurant as a whole.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(33, 791, 'George', 'george.olaru@pixelgrade.com', 'http://pixelgrade.com', '5.2.190.30', '2015-11-06 13:31:20', '2015-11-06 13:31:20', 'SCP is the kind of place that most of us will never buy anything from but will nonetheless enjoy roaming through the store. Furniture in here is so stylish it would only suit a very specific style of house and a very full wallet for that matter!', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(34, 801, 'henry stainton', 'henry@tihh.co.uk', '', '213.133.138.5', '2015-11-18 10:34:17', '2015-11-18 10:34:17', 'Along with office buildings and residential apartments, Paddington Central is also home to a gym, a number of quick lunch stops cafes as well as several canal side bars and restaurants. Enjoy a lunchtime run along Regent’s Canal, an almost traffic-free jog through the heart and soul of London.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(35, 250, 'George Olaru', 'george.olaru@pixelgrade.com', 'http://pixelgrade.com', '5.2.190.30', '2015-10-20 12:32:10', '2015-10-20 12:32:10', 'Thank you for those tips! The search engines optimizations made it easy to try this hidden gem. Try their house-made bread with chocolate.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0);

